		<title>OmniRetail, M-KOPA, Sabi, TymeBank make FT’s Africa fastest-growing companies list</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/12/30-startups-on-ft-africas-fastest-growing-companies-list/</link>
		
